latestIgtvVideos.title: HOW WOULD I STYLE MY OUTFITS, IF I WAS:
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s to the Women who helped us shape our careers as Independent Content Creators, be it in Fashion, Make Up, Travel or Lifestyle as a whole. I remember there was a time when the term ‘Influencer’ was frowned upon, Internet fame seemed shallow, Artists were considered ‘too old school’. It’s amazing how these young women changed our small perspectives and proved themselves successful. They have been a major source of inspiration when I finally decided to turn my career overall. I’m so glad to have come across these beautiful souls whose faith in themselves gave hope to thousands of girls like me. 
This women’s day I decided to give a little tribute to these wonderful women. I hope they come across this video and hopefully it’ll make them smile. ♥️
 
🌼 @thelazyinsomniac 
🌷 @debasreee 
🌺 @larissa_wlc 

Song: Girl Like Me by Black Eyed Peas, Shakira. 🎶
